➜湖北诗人木子：一叶落·秋感  （二首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/416135931_100115135	36160
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/4b998a7667ce41a5885bf89ff7bfa523.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一叶落：秋感</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一叶落，西风恶，此情最怕景萧索。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">且看雁阵归，方知人情薄。人情薄，不负今生约。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200902/e4ddb744a06046ca9bfc5f3f33566c47.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>二</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一叶落，衣衫薄。紫陌芳园景如昨。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">莫悲柳影寒，秋来诗乡约，诗乡约，恰是云天阔。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/670f7df7d7fb47bb888e51503e9dcfbf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
