➜河南诗人田书芹：念
http://www.sohu.com/a/416136310_100115135	36421
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200902/22ec3b406ccd45a88f336c4800697e5c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>念</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文／田书芹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">煮一壶茶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在夕阳里等你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">黄昏的阳格外的迷人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">四射的光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落在窗前的玉兰花上。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>桌上的茶还温热，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>随手把那些已久的心事，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>泡在茶里浸润，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>融散，沉淀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清晰的记忆里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你一直都在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为，有牵挂，期盼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心就不会再寂凉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.9.2</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200902/971f6f1fc3af4815a70e648b2f16a884.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
